<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>訂閱電子報</title>
  <style>
    section {
      margin: 1em 10%;
    }
  </style>
  <script>
    function defaultFocus() {
      document.getElementById("userName").focus();
    }
  </script>
</head>

<body onLoad='defaultFocus()'>
  <section>
    <header>
      <hr>
      <h2>訂閱電子報</h2>
      <hr>
    </header>
    <p>免費訂閱產業相關消息與研討會訊息， 請輸入您的姓名與電子郵件：</p>
    <form action="/subscribe" method="get">
      <table border="0">
        <tr>
          <td><label for="userName">姓名： </label></td>
          <td><input type="text" id="userName" name="userName" required></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><label for="userEmail">電郵： </label></td>
          <td><input type="email" id="userEmail" name="userEmail" required></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td><input type="submit" /></td>
      </table>
    </form>
  </section>
</body>

</html>